name: concepts
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "concepts" %}
{% set version = "0.9.2" %}

package:
  name: "{{ name|lower }}"
  version: "{{ version }}"

source:
  url: "https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.zip"
  sha256: 8bbfa9ffdf89cc6e13c79a902474086797500b31d043604aa1d63bfe5faada2c

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv"

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python
  run:
    - bitsets >=0.7,<1
    - python-graphviz >=0.7,<1
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - concepts

about:
  home: https://github.com/xflr6/concepts
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE.txt
  summary: "Formal Concept Analysis with Python"
  doc_url: https://concepts.readthedocs.io/en/stable/
  dev_url: https://github.com/xflr6/concepts

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - npavlovikj
